OL,3,CPeople's politician or political
OL,4,Cschemer? Locals divided over Burnham
OL,6,FLocals in Ashton-in-Makerfield have
OL,7,Fvoiced mixed opinions on Andy
OL,8,FBurnham's bid to become their next MP,
OL,9,Fwith some celebrating his experience
OL,10,Fand big-name status, while others
OL,11,Fquestion the fairness of a high-
OL,12,Fprofile "parachuting" into the
OL,13,Fconstituency.
OL,15,FThe Mayor of Greater Manchester
OL,16,Fconfirmed he will be seeking to stand
OL,17,Fas the Labour candidate on Thursday 15
OL,18,FMay after the current MP Josh Simons
OL,19,Fannounced he'll be standing down to
OL,20,Fprovide Andy Burnham with a route back
OL,21,Fto Westminster.
OL,26,@tD@IOUtD@UO]
