OL,3,CPeople's politician or political
OL,4,Cschemer? Locals divided over Burnham
OL,6,FAs he had a drink in his local pub,
OL,7,FMark said he was "disappointed" that
OL,8,Fthe previous MP had stepped down, and
OL,9,Fcriticised the idea of Burnham being
OL,10,F"parachuted" in.
OL,12,FHe said: "I think people from the
OL,13,Flocal area should know the issues and
OL,14,Fbe able to deal with them. He spends
OL,15,Fmore time in the centre of Manchester,
OL,16,Fdoesn't he?"
OL,18,FWhile he believes Burnham could "save
OL,19,Fthe Labour Party," he doubts the party
OL,20,Fwould continue to thrive beyond a year
OL,21,For two under his leadership.
OL,26,@oD@ROUoD@_O]rD@AOUrD@LO]tD@JOUxD@LO]zD@
OL,26,AaOU{D@RO]
