OL,3,CPeople's politician or political
OL,4,Cschemer? Locals divided over Burnham
OL,6,FHe said: "I quite like Andy Burnham as
OL,7,Fa person. He speaks a lot of sense,
OL,8,Fbut if somebody just comes along and
OL,9,Ftakes a seat, it doesn't feel quite
OL,10,Fright to me. We had a perfectly good
OL,11,FMP."
OL,13,F"I think people will vote for him
OL,14,Fbecause he's very popular and a decent
OL,15,Fguy, but I don't know how good that
OL,16,Fwill be for this constituency... Is it
OL,17,Fa political game?"
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@DO]yD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
