OL,3,CPeople's politician or political
OL,4,Cschemer? Locals divided over Burnham
OL,6,FAnother local, Harry, welcomed
OL,7,FBurnham's candidacy, saying, "I think
OL,8,Fit's good. You should just get the big
OL,9,Fnames, they will represent us on a big
OL,10,Fstage."
OL,12,FDespite being disillusioned with
OL,13,Fpolitics, Harry felt a big name like
OL,14,FBurnham could inspire engagement, he
OL,15,Fsaid: "Just having a big name
OL,16,Frepresenting you in Parliament, I
OL,17,Fthink just go for it, see what
OL,18,Fhappens."
OL,26,@oD@^OUrD@GO]wD@GOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
