OL,3,CPeople's politician or political
OL,4,Cschemer? Locals divided over Burnham
OL,6,FChristine was also enthusiastic about
OL,7,FBurnham, she said: "I would love Andy
OL,8,FBurnham to be our MP. He's done a
OL,9,Fmassive amount of work for
OL,10,Fhomelessness in Manchester. He's a
OL,11,Fpeople's man, and I think he's
OL,12,Ffantastic."
OL,14,FOn whether Burnham could save Labour,
OL,15,Fshe added: "I think he could turn it
OL,16,Faround massively. He is a people's man
OL,17,Fnow."
OL,26,@oD@TOUtD@KO]wD@LOUyD@EO]
