OL,3,CPeople's politician or political
OL,4,Cschemer? Locals divided over Burnham
OL,6,FChloe shared a positive experience of
OL,7,Fher encounter with Andy Burnham, she
OL,8,Fsaid: "I quite like Andy Burnham. When
OL,9,FI was in school, he really helped with
OL,10,Fthe community. I think he'll bring
OL,11,Fmore power and structure to Ashton-in-
OL,12,FMakerfield."
OL,14,FShe hopes that with community support,
OL,15,FBurnham could do well and potentially
OL,16,Fhelp revive the Labour Party.
OL,26,@pD@GOUtD@LO]
